  "notes": "Shares its core behaviour with the Nukem, but World Burn is always incendiary, consumes 1 rocket per shot, and generally offers higher base damage, a larger magazine, and slower reloads. It can roll different accessories but never gets a prefix. A rocket-velocity part boosts effective range while flattening the arc, making indirect shots over cover harder. Maya's Accelerate and Zer0's Vel0city help at medium to long range. Lt. Bolson has a 20% drop chance.",
